cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is about visual tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a novel architecture for tracking, which involves deep learning techniques, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories. Additionally, the paper deals with robotics and autonomous systems, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics) category. Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on popular tracking benchmarks, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) category.
